## Article

```catala
declaration f
  content boolean
  depends on x content integer
  equals
    if x = 0 then false else true

declaration scope ScopeA:
  input i content boolean
  output f_scope_a content boolean depends on x content integer
  output a_scopeA content boolean

scope ScopeA:
  definition f_scope_a of x equals
    match (if x = 3 then Absent else Present content 3) with pattern
    -- Absent : false
    -- anything : true
  definition a_scopeA equals i

declaration scope ScopeB:
  output a_scopeB content boolean
  ssv scope ScopeA
  internal g content boolean depends on x content integer
  output res content ScopeA

scope ScopeB:
  definition ssv.i equals let zzz equals 333 in true

  label base
  definition a_scopeB equals ssv.a_scopeA

  label one exception base
  definition a_scopeB
  under condition 42 = 42
  consequence equals
    not ssv.a_scopeA

  label two exception one
  definition a_scopeB
  under condition 43 > 43
  consequence equals
    not (ssv.f_scope_a of 2 or ssv.a_scopeA)

  definition g of x equals
    match (if x = 3 then Absent else Present content 3) with pattern
    -- Absent : false
    -- anything : true

  definition res equals
    output of ScopeA with { -- i: f of 2 or g of 3 }

  assertion 42 = 42
```

